data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!  Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 Bath Home. When you walk in you will at once feel right at home and yet also elegant- from the formal living room with fireplace to the formal dining room with its chandelier, european paneling, and large window. The kitchen features a microwave, breakfast bar and an ample breakfast area with plenty of pantry in the adjacent utility area. This also gives access to the large covered patio with ceiling fan and a storage shed/workshop. The master is on the lower level with large windows and a huge walk in closet with built-ins. Each of the 3 spacious upstairs bedrooms come with ceiling fans and each floor has its own Heating and Cooling units. Easily maintain your large lot and beautiful, mature shade trees with the 8 zone automatic sprinkler system. Inside you'll maintain a sense of well being and security with your ADT security system.  The back entrance to the huge Purser Family Park is directly at the end of the street on one end and Mountain View Elementary is just a minute or two walking distance the other direction. You will be enchanted with this lovely home and all it has to offer, and, great news!! It’s available for you now!
